Description: Oh my goodness! This "Sheba" laptop bag designed by Maddie Powers is to die for. If you're college-bound this week or have a job in tech where you can rock this bag, it's a must-have. Excellent padded protection for your laptop (up to a 14.1" screen). Soft shoulder strap.
